---
title: Garlic Steak With Cranberry Pan Sauce plus Sweet Potato–Parsnip Mash & Dijon Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: As a rule, we love any meal we can brighten up with a show-stopping sauce, and this garlicky seared steak is no exception. It’s drizzled with a tangy-savory-sweet cranberry-infused garlic butter pan sauce, while the Brussels sprouts on the side get just as much love—tossed in a tangy Dijon vinaigrette and sprinkled with Parmesan. A rustic sweet potato and parsnip mash completes this trio of deliciousness that’s packed with bold flavors.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6581ed266140de482b9ce623-83542a2a.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6581ed266140de482b9ce623.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/garlic-steak-with-cranberry-pan-sauce-6581ed266140de482b9ce623
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 1110 kcal
  fat: 74 g
